g.text: You know the game is rigged. You see the housing crisis,
the wealth extraction, and the ecological collapse.
You have the passion. You have the anger.
But you are losing.
For twenty years, we have brought passion to a logistics fight.
We relied on shame and protest, while the oligarchy relied
on asset inflation and algorithmic attention harvesting.
Radical Competence is the strategy manual for the
counter-offensive. It bridges the gap between the desire
for justice and the capacity for execution.

ABOUT THE AUTHOR
Björn Kenneth Holmström is a systems thinker and
architect of the Global Governance Frameworks initiative.
His mission is to contribute to the redesign of civilization
for the liberation of all beings. Drawing from engineering
physics and optimization, he builds the operating systems
that make human flourishing structurally possible.
He writes and thinks from Stockholm, Sweden.
